# Implementation Plan Summary

The project will be built iteratively:
1. Setup Python project structure.
2. Implement backend database and models (SQLite).
3. Set up backend HTTP server to serve static files.
4. Create basic frontend shell (HTML, Alpine.js, DaisyUI).
5. Build backend API endpoints (CRUD for commands, toggle state).
6. Integrate frontend with API.
7. Add backend speech recognition.
8. Implement backend WebSocket for real-time updates.
9. Integrate frontend WebSocket.
10. Implement backend script parsing and execution.
11. Refine and test thoroughly.

For the detailed step-by-step plan, see: [plan.md](mdc:memory-bank/plan.md)

